@Reasoning:
External integration hook callable from a top-level test runner.
Returns the all-suites-passed signal from run_all_tests.
@End Reasoning

@Implementation:
Forward to run_all_tests() and return its result.
@End Implementation

Process called "test_verilog_translation" that takes nothing returns Integer:
    Return proc run_all_tests
End Process
